Exame Época Normal 21/22

1. 

	a) cat /etc/passwd | cut -d ":" -f1,3 | sort -k2 -n | tail -2 | head -1 

	b) ls -l /etc | cut -d " " -f5,9 | sort -k1 -n | tail -5 > ~/ficheiros.txt
______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Exame Época de Recurso 21/22

1.

	a) cat /etc/passwd | sort -t ":" -k3 -n | tail -12 | sort -t ":" -k1 | cut -d ":" -f1 > ~/novatos.txt

	b) ls -l /tmp | tr -s " " | cut -d " " -f1,5,9 | grep "^-r?xrw?---" | sort -n -r | head -n 1 | cut -d " " -f3 | wc -c

