Exame Época Normal 23/24

4. ls -l | tr -s " " | cut -d " " -f5,9 | sort -k1 -n | tail -5 | cut -d " " -f1 > ~/maiores.txt

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Exame Época de Recurso 23/24

4. cat /etc/passwd | cut -d ":" -f1,3,6 | sort -k2 -n | tail -3 | head -2 | sort -k2 -n -r | cut -d ":" -f1,3 > ~/listagem.txt

